This was originally my final project for CMSC405, "Computer Graphics." It was a
class on OpenGL. 

Download image data: http://bumba.net/~hmaon/amazeballs/data.zip






Building on Linux:

A Makefile is included. 

You need freeglut, SDL, SDL_mixer, and SDL_image to build. On Ubuntu, the
packages required are libsdl-mixer1.2-dev, libsdl-image1.2-dev, freeglut3-dev.


Building on Windows:

You need libs and DLLs.
http://bumba.net/~hmaon/amazeballs/amazeballs_windows_libs.7z

-- greg v.
